PARAM_ITEM.PARAM_DESCRIPTION:
Optional argument : Shape of the structuring element; may have the following values:
SHAPE_RECT , a rectangular element; 
SHAPE_CROSS , a cross-shaped element; 
SHAPE_ELLIPSE , an elliptic element;

MAN.EXAMPLE:
//upgrade the size of the memory
stacksize(10000000); 

//load the picture
B=imread('/home/vincent/software/sivp/images/lena.tif');

//call the SIVP function
A=erode(B,2);
//A=erode(B,3,'RECT',3,3,1,1);
//A=erode(B,4,'CROSS',3,3,1,1);
//A=erode(B,5,'ELLIPSE',3,3,1,1);

//conversion
A=double(A)/255;

//try to display the result
imshow(A);
